{
  "id": "RAW_dd9b91cb",
  "title": "React 入门秘籍：像搭积木一样写网页，JSX 让开发爽到飞起！",
  "url": "https://juejin.cn/post/7582863493259345972",
  "date": "2025-12-13 04:24:15",
  "author": "风止何安啊",
  "siteName": "掘金本周最热",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"article-viewer markdown-body result\">\n   <h2 data-id=\"heading-0\">前言</h2>\n   <p>还在为原生 JS 写页面 “东拼西凑” 头疼？还在为 HTML 和 JS 交互写一堆繁琐逻辑？好了，我们聊了这么久的 <code>JS</code>，相信大家对 JS 已经有了一定的基础了。接下来我们开始接触前端框架，带大家了解--<code>React</code>。</p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p>具体<code>JS</code>学习请看我的专栏：<a href=\"https://juejin.cn/column/7568769772507775016\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://juejin.cn/column/7568769772507775016\">你不知道的JavaScript</a></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-1\">一、React：让前端开发效率翻倍的 JS 框架</h3>\n   <p>相信学习前端的小伙伴对<code>React</code>这个词并不陌生，但又不知道它具体是个啥。大白话来讲，它就是<strong>让 JS 开发 “开挂” 的框架</strong>。简单来说，<code>React</code> 就是来 “救场” 的<strong>JS 框架</strong>！它把网页拆成 “组件”，像搭积木一样拼出整个页面，还能用<strong>JSX</strong>把 JS 和 HTML 揉在一起写，直接让开发效率起飞～</p>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-2\">二、开局第一步：搭建 React 项目环境</h3>\n   <p>想玩转<code>React</code>，先把开发环境搭好！主流有两种方式，按需选择：</p>\n   <h4 data-id=\"heading-3\">1. <strong>create-react-app</strong>：官方 “傻瓜式” 脚手架</h4>\n   <p>React 官方推出的项目创建工具，无需手动配置 webpack、babel 等底层工具，一行命令就能生成完整的 React 项目：</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-bash code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"bash\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 创建项目</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">npx create-react-app my-react-app</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 进入项目目录</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">cd</span> my-react-app</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 启动项目</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">npm start</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p>优点是省心、稳定，适合 React 新手入门；缺点是项目体积较大，启动速度稍慢。</p>\n   <h4 data-id=\"heading-4\">2. <strong>Vite</strong>：新一代 “极速” 构建工具</h4>\n   <p>如今更推荐的轻量化选择，启动速度、热更新效率远超传统脚手架，创建 React 项目更高效:</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-bash code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"bash\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 创建Vite+React项目</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">npm create vite@latest   <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># latest是选择最新版本</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 你创建的项目名字</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">my-vite-react</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 选择 React JavaScript 然后一路Enter</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 进入目录</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">cd</span> my-vite-react</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"12\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 安装依赖</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"13\">npm install</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"14\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"15\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 启动项目</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"16\">npm run dev</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/4b22c9360dbd4bbc82aa5a23d56b00f3~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg6aOO5q2i5L2V5a6J5ZWK:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1766204655&amp;x-signature=ZTd8YZpUOvdc4OunYYR1BwIa0%2Bo%3D\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p>启动后就能看到 Vite 默认的 React 项目结构，核心入口文件就是<code>main.jsx</code>—— 这是整个 React 项目的最外层入口，所有组件最终都会通过它挂载到页面上。</p>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-5\">三、JSX：React 的 “语法糖”，让 JS 和 HTML 无缝融合</h3>\n   <p>JSX 的本质是 “JS + XML（HTML）”，看似写 HTML，实则是 JS 的语法扩展，用它写界面比原生 JS 简洁 10 倍！但使用时要遵守核心规则：</p>\n   <h4 data-id=\"heading-6\">1. 核心规则：JSX 里只能放 “表达式”，不能放 “语句”</h4>\n   <ul>\n    <li><strong>表达式</strong>：有返回值的代码（比如变量、算术运算、数组方法、三元运算），用<code>{}</code>包裹就能嵌入 JSX；</li>\n    <li><strong>语句</strong>：无返回值的执行逻辑（比如 if、for 循环），不能直接写在 JSX 里，需转换为表达式形式。</li>\n   </ul>\n   <h4 data-id=\"heading-7\">2. 实战 1：列表循环渲染（核心高频场景）</h4>\n   <p>原生 JS 写列表需要手动创建 DOM、循环追加，代码繁琐：</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-html code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"html\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">ul</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">id</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"ul\"</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">&lt;!-- 得写 for 循环 + createElement + appendChild --&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">script</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"javascript\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> arr = [<span class=\"hljs-string\">'1'</span>,<span class=\"hljs-string\">'2'</span>,<span class=\"hljs-string\">'3'</span>];</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 手动循环 + 创建 DOM，代码冗余</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; i &lt; arr.<span class=\"hljs-property\">length</span>; i++) {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> li = <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">document</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">createElement</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">'li'</span>);</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">        li.<span class=\"hljs-property\">textContent</span> = arr[i];</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\">        <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">document</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">getElementById</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">'ul'</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">appendChild</span>(li);</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\">    }</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"12\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">script</span>&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p>这种原生写法用起来就非常麻烦，而且代码也多。但 React 的<strong>JSX + 列表渲染</strong>，直接 “声明” 要渲染的内容，React 自动帮你生成 DOM：</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-jsx code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"jsx\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">App</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> arr = [<span class=\"hljs-string\">'1'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">'2'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">'3'</span>];</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// map是表达式，返回新数组，可直接嵌入JSX</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> (</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">        <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">ul</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">id</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"ul\"</span>&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">            {arr.map((item, index) =&gt; (</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">                <span class=\"hljs-comment\">&lt;!-- 循环渲染必须加 key，唯一标识每一项 --&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">                <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">li</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">key</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">{index}</span>&gt;</span>{item}<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">            ))}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\">        <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\">    );</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"12\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p>进阶版：渲染复杂数据列表:</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-jsx code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"jsx\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">App</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> songs = [</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">        { <span class=\"hljs-attr\">id</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">name</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'稻香'</span> },</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">        { <span class=\"hljs-attr\">id</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">name</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'夜曲'</span> },</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">        { <span class=\"hljs-attr\">id</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">name</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'晴天'</span> }</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">    ];</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> (</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">        <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">            {songs.map((item) =&gt; (</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\">                <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">li</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">key</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">{item.id}</span>&gt;</span>{item.name}<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\">            ))}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"12\">        <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"13\">    );</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"14\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/76af099ce99c432790622e3f8ae70842~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg6aOO5q2i5L2V5a6J5ZWK:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1766204655&amp;x-signature=WKVqLrfAhfxpIPss7cy91p9fMig%3D\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <h4 data-id=\"heading-8\">3. 实战 2：条件渲染（按需展示界面）</h4>\n   <p><strong>需求</strong>：根据条件展示不同内容，不能直接写 if 语句，用三元表达式（表达式）实现：</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-jsx code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"jsx\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">App</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> flag = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> (</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">        <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">            {/* 三元表达式是表达式，可嵌入JSX */}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">h2</span>&gt;</span>{flag ? '我比他帅' : '他比我帅'}<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">h2</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">            {/* 进阶：逻辑与运算，flag为true时才显示 */}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">p</span>&gt;</span>{flag &amp;&amp; '只有flag为真才显示我'}<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">p</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">        <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\">    );</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/fb7c7afac1ca4f97ac779a70316a444a~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg6aOO5q2i5L2V5a6J5ZWK:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1766204655&amp;x-signature=4tHxw7Z99C3GgFwmf6nxOXiAbmo%3D\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <h4 data-id=\"heading-9\">4. 实战 3：样式处理（三种常用方式）</h4>\n   <p>JSX 中写样式和原生 HTML 有区别，结合图片中样式代码，三种方式全覆盖：</p>\n   <p><strong>（1）行内样式（对象形式）</strong></p>\n   <p>原生 HTML 用<code>style=\"color: red\"</code>，JSX 需用对象包裹，属性名用<strong>小驼峰</strong>：</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-jsx code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"jsx\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">App</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> styleObj = { </span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'red'</span>, </span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">fontSize</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'20px'</span> <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 小驼峰，对应 CSS 的 font-size</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">    };</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> (</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">        <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">style</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">{styleObj}</span>&gt;</span>帅哥<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">            {/* 也可直接写对象 */}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\">            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">style</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">{{</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">color:</span> '<span class=\"hljs-attr\">blue</span>', <span class=\"hljs-attr\">fontWeight:</span> '<span class=\"hljs-attr\">bold</span>' }}&gt;</span>帅哥<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\">        <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"12\">    );</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"13\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p>这里提一嘴，<code>JSX</code>表达式必须要有一个父元素！</p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/69e793da449d4edf98b1d69011a40fe7~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg6aOO5q2i5L2V5a6J5ZWK:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1766204655&amp;x-signature=HZN%2BDsZIznzlll5ZsNJ4Z%2FdZIsY%3D\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/eef9470246c74d519a9b3e9d410d9dd3~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg6aOO5q2i5L2V5a6J5ZWK:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1766204655&amp;x-signature=KTxVUGtYqAEUeiLj5UDtDYD%2B0Gg%3D\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p><strong>(2）类名样式（className）</strong></p>\n   <p>JSX 中不能用<code>class</code>（保留字），需用<code>className</code>，配合 CSS 文件：</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-css code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"css\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* index.css */</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.home</span> {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">    <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#f5f5f5</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">    <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">padding</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">20px</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-jsx code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"jsx\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// App.jsx</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">'./index.css'</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">App</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">className</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"home\"</span>&gt;</span>首页<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 对应图片中 className 代码</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/71603c9b9bbf4a29b09eeb942e5962ec~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg6aOO5q2i5L2V5a6J5ZWK:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1766204655&amp;x-signature=7pdqoK8e4wiAuinRmRSX5leTaPc%3D\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"> <strong>（3）动态类名</strong></p>\n   <p>结合表达式，按需切换样式：</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-jsx code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"jsx\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">App</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> isActive = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> (</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">        <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">className</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">{</span>`<span class=\"hljs-attr\">box</span> ${<span class=\"hljs-attr\">isActive</span> ? '<span class=\"hljs-attr\">active</span>' <span class=\"hljs-attr\">:</span> ''}`}&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">            动态样式</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">        <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">    );</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <h4 data-id=\"heading-10\">5. 实战 4：事件绑定（交互核心）</h4>\n   <p>原生 HTML 用<code>onclick</code>，JSX 用小驼峰<code>onClick</code>，且绑定的是函数（而非字符串）:</p>\n   <p><strong>（1）基础事件绑定</strong></p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-jsx code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"jsx\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">App</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 定义事件处理函数</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">handleClick</span> = (<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) =&gt; {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">        <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">'点击了div'</span>);</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">    };</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> (</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 直接绑定函数，不加()（加()会立即执行）</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">        <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">onClick</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">{handleClick}</span>&gt;</span>hello<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">    );</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/371f427664454686a2795adb199939a0~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg6aOO5q2i5L2V5a6J5ZWK:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1766204655&amp;x-signature=RJeyFDTVd%2F08dC7DpESo6xKOUx0%3D\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <p><strong>（2）事件传参</strong></p>\n   <p>需用箭头函数包裹，才能传递参数：</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-jsx code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"jsx\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">App5</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> songs = [</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">        { <span class=\"hljs-attr\">id</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">name</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'稻香'</span> },</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">        { <span class=\"hljs-attr\">id</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">name</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'夜曲'</span> }</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">    ];</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 带参数的事件函数</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">handler</span> = (<span class=\"hljs-params\">name</span>) =&gt; {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">        <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">'点击了歌曲：'</span>, name);</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">    };</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> (</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\">        <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"12\">            {songs.map((item) =&gt; (</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"13\">                <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">li</span> </span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"14\">                    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">key</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">{item.id}</span> </span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"15\">                    // <span class=\"hljs-attr\">箭头函数传参</span>，<span class=\"hljs-attr\">点击时执行handler并传入歌曲名</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"16\">                    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">onClick</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">{()</span> =&gt; handler(item.name)}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"17\">                &gt;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"18\">                    {item.name}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"19\">                <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"20\">            ))}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"21\">        <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"22\">    );</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"23\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/6dd3b6c5e6e14ace95e8bb45b7a4a319~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg6aOO5q2i5L2V5a6J5ZWK:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1766204655&amp;x-signature=zbYjRp5BKFEH%2BR98P%2B3WD1cIH1c%3D\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-11\">四、组件化：React 的 “灵魂”，像搭积木一样开发</h3>\n   <p>组件化是 React 单页应用的核心，把页面拆成独立、可复用的组件，比如头部、导航、内容区，再像搭积木一样组合。</p>\n   <h4 data-id=\"heading-12\">1. 定义组件（两种方式）</h4>\n   <p><strong>（1）函数组件（推荐）</strong></p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-jsx code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"jsx\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// components/Head.jsx（头部组件）</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">Head</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> (</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">        <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">header</span>&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">h1</span>&gt;</span>我的React博客<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">h1</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">nav</span>&gt;</span>首页 | 文章 | 关于<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">nav</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">        <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">header</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">    );</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// components/Main.jsx（主体组件）</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"12\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">Main</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"13\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> songs = [{ <span class=\"hljs-attr\">id</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">name</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'稻香'</span> }, { <span class=\"hljs-attr\">id</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">name</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'夜曲'</span> }];</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"14\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> (</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"15\">        <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">main</span>&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"16\">          <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">h2</span>&gt;</span>热门歌曲<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">h2</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"17\">          <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"18\">            {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"19\">              songs.map(item =&gt; <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">li</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">key</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">{item.id}</span>&gt;</span>{item.name}<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">li</span>&gt;</span>)</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"20\">            }</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"21\">          <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"22\">        <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">main</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"23\">    );</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"24\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p><strong>（2）组合组件（拼装页面）</strong></p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-jsx code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"jsx\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// App.jsx（根组件）</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Head</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">'./components/Head'</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Main</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">'./components/Main'</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">App6</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> (</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">        <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">className</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"app\"</span>&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">            {/* 引入头部组件 */}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">Head</span> /&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\">            {/* 引入主体组件 */}</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\">            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">Main</span> /&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"12\">        <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"13\">    );</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"14\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/e296347cb1914402a22a7304728f0c49~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg6aOO5q2i5L2V5a6J5ZWK:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1766204655&amp;x-signature=RCypS7p009KTF5VHjzZvnp1CHv0%3D\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <h4 data-id=\"heading-13\">2. 组件渲染到页面（入口文件）</h4>\n   <p>所有组件最终要通过<code>main.jsx</code>挂载到 DOM 节点：</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-jsx code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"jsx\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// main.jsx（项目最外层入口）</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">React</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">'react'</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ReactDOM</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">'react-dom/client'</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">App</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">'./App.jsx'</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">'./index.css'</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 找到页面中的root节点，渲染App根组件</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\"><span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ReactDOM</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">createRoot</span>(<span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">document</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">getElementById</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">'root'</span>)).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">render</span>(</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">    <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">React.StrictMode</span>&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\">        <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">App</span> /&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">React.StrictMode</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"12\">);</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-14\">五、JSX 进阶：数组处理小技巧</h3>\n   <p>开发中常需要对数组做转换，比如把数字数组放大 10 倍（比如我们在<strong>实战1</strong> 中使用的 <code>map</code>）：</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-jsx code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"jsx\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">App</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> arr = [<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>];</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// map返回新数组，可直接渲染或赋值使用</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> newArr = arr.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">map</span>(<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-params\">item</span> =&gt;</span> item * <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>);</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> (</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"6\">        <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"7\">            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">p</span>&gt;</span>原数组：{arr.join(',')}<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">p</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"8\">            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">p</span>&gt;</span>放大10倍:{newArr.join(',')}<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">p</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"9\">        <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"10\">    );</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"11\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p>放在 JS 里可能更好理解：</p>\n   <pre><code class=\"hljs language-javascript code-block-extension-codeShowNum\" lang=\"javascript\"><span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"1\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> arr = [<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>];</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"2\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> newArr = arr.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">map</span>(<span class=\"hljs-function\">(<span class=\"hljs-params\">item, i, array</span>) =&gt;</span> {  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// [10, 20, 30, 40]</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"3\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> item * <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>;</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"4\">})</span>\n<span class=\"code-block-extension-codeLine\" data-line-num=\"5\"><span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(newArr);</span>\n</code></pre>\n   <p><img src=\"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/aa5b62d2b5fa4116a40a60cfe35cae27~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg6aOO5q2i5L2V5a6J5ZWK:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1766204655&amp;x-signature=htcd%2BGJ%2FWMr7xhoFtJHEG1VdDCM%3D\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"medium-zoom-image\"></p>\n   <h3 data-id=\"heading-15\">六、总结：React 开发核心流程</h3>\n   <p><strong>1.</strong> 用<code>create-react-app</code>或<code>Vite</code>创建项目；</p>\n   <p><strong>2.</strong> 在<code>main.jsx</code>中挂载根组件<code>App</code>；</p>\n   <p><strong>3.</strong> 拆分子组件（Head、Main 等），用 JSX 编写组件逻辑；</p>\n   <p><strong>4.</strong> 合表达式实现列表渲染、条件渲染、样式处理、事件绑定；</p>\n   <p><strong>5.</strong> 组合组件，完成整个页面开发。</p>\n   <h2 data-id=\"heading-16\">结语</h2>\n   <p><code>React</code> 的核心就是 <strong>“简单”</strong>：用 JSX 简化 HTML 和 JS 的交互，用组件化简化页面结构，用声明式 UI 简化 DOM 操作。把这些基础知识点吃透，再结合代码例子实战反复练习，你就能从 React 新手快速进阶！</p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文为 React 初学者提供了全面的入门指南，详细介绍了 React 框架的核心概念、开发环境搭建、JSX 语法及其在列表渲染、条件渲染、样式处理和事件绑定中的实际应用，并通过组件化思想指导读者构建页面。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文为 React 初学者提供了全面的入门指南，详细介绍了 React 框架的核心概念、开发环境搭建、JSX 语法及其在列表渲染、条件渲染、样式处理和事件绑定中的实际应用，并通过组件化思想指导读者构建页面。",
  "summary": "文章旨在帮助前端初学者快速上手 React 开发。首先，它解释了 React 作为 JavaScript 框架如何通过组件化和 JSX 提高开发效率。接着，介绍了两种主要的 React 项目环境搭建方式：create-react-app（适合新手）和 Vite（更高效）。文章重点阐述了 JSX 的核心规则，即只能嵌入表达式，并结合实战案例详细讲解了如何使用 JSX 进行列表渲染、条件渲染、样式处理和事件绑定。最后，强调了 React 组件化的思想，指导读者如何定义和组合组件构建完整的页面。通过详细的代码示例和图解，文章为读者提供了清晰实用的 React 基础知识。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "React 通过组件化和 JSX 大幅提升前端开发效率。",
      "explanation": "React 将复杂页面拆分为独立、可复用的组件，并通过 JSX 将 JavaScript 和 HTML 融合，简化了 UI 开发，让开发者能像搭积木一样高效构建页面，显著优于传统原生 JS 开发方式。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Vite 是更高效的 React 项目构建工具，适合快速开发和热更新。",
      "explanation": "相比 create-react-app，Vite 在项目启动速度和热更新效率上表现更优，推荐现代 React 项目选择 Vite 进行环境搭建，能够提升开发体验。"
    },
    {
      "point": "JSX 的核心规则是只允许嵌入表达式，并且提供了灵活的 UI 控制能力。",
      "explanation": "开发者需理解 JSX 中只能放置返回值（如变量、三元表达式、数组方法）的表达式，而不能直接使用语句（如 if、for），这一特性是实现声明式 UI 的基础，并可应用于列表渲染、条件渲染等高频场景。"
    },
    {
      "point": "React 组件化是构建可维护、可复用前端应用的关键。",
      "explanation": "将页面划分为独立的函数组件，并通过根组件进行组合，不仅提高了代码的可维护性和复用性，也使得团队协作和项目扩展变得更加高效和有序。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "React 就是来 '救场' 的 JS 框架！它把网页拆成 '组件'，像搭积木一样拼出整个页面，还能用 JSX 把 JS 和 HTML 揉在一起写，直接让开发效率起飞～",
    "JSX 的本质是 'JS + XML（HTML）'，看似写 HTML，实则是 JS 的语法扩展，用它写界面比原生 JS 简洁 10 倍！",
    "组件化是 React 单页应用的核心，把页面拆成独立、可复用的组件，比如头部、导航、内容区，再像搭积木一样组合。",
    "React 的核心就是 '简单'：用 JSX 简化 HTML 和 JS 的交互，用组件化简化页面结构，用声明式 UI 简化 DOM 操作。"
  ],
